high_descs: Go left to the refrigerator on the left
Open the door and take the tomato from the top shelf
Turn left and go to the microwave
Open the microwave, place the tomato in the center, close the door then open it and take the tomato out of the microwave
Turn left and go the the sink on the right
Place the tomato in the sink on the right
anns.task_desc: Microwave the tomato and put it in the sink

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Pick up the tomato from the top shelf in the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Microwave the tomato and then pick the tomato up from the microwave.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the tomato in the sink on the right.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Go left and turn left at the door to walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge, remove the chilled tomato from the top shelf and close the door.
Head left and turn to the microwave on the counter to the right side.
Put the tomato inside the microwave on the black plate, heat it for a few seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the heated tomato in the sink on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato in a sink.
